nodes.caption: Failure is a necessary part of growth, and in the process of realizing your dreams. Failure is never fatal and it's not a dead end. Failure leads you to an unexpected reward, if you're receptive. Failure is nothing more than consistent incorrect actions, as a result of an error in judgement, over an extended period of time. When we stop for a minute to evaluate why what we're doing isn't working, we open up the door to receive the formula to make that step in the process work. Failure will only defeat a quitter, but failure is the launching pad for a winner. A winner will take what there is to learn from the failure and use it to correct the course, thus implementing the proper actions as a result of corrected judgement. Actions implemented from correct judgement over and extended period of time has no choice but to yield success in the long run. Don't be afraid of failure. Failure is what is needed to learn and grow.
